name: I Hate Monday
description:
This illustration is based on a true story when I worked in a metropolitan city. Monday is a day that I really hate, because I have to work. not because of his job, but about his journey. have to leave early to catch the train early. Inside the train must be jostling, wallet in pickpocket, fight with each other. other passengers.
haha, this is true. and this illustration is to remind you that I've been in that position, maybe you too!


_ "Long Life Hardworker" _

3000 x 2000 px
500DPI
